        public static RequestExternalPayment.Request newInstance(java.lang.String instanceId,
                                                         java.lang.String patternId,
                                                         java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> params)
        Creates instance of payment's request for general purposes. In other words for payments to a specific pattern_id with known parameters. Take a look at subclasses of PaymentParams especially for p2p and phone-topup payments.
        Parameters:
        instanceId - application's instance id.
        patternId - pattern_id (p2p, phone-topup or shop).
        params - payment parameters.
        Returns:
        new request instance.
